GAJAK

Gajak Sweets prepared with til (sesame seedsm), Ghee, Jaggery or Sugar, Kaju (in particular variant only). Gajak sweets carry the authentic taste and aura of Morena within their texture. It is said that it is due to some components in the water of the Chambal river that a sweet came to be developed from it. The gajaks of Morena are very well-known and is exported internationally. Order from our wide range of Gajak sweets verities and lift up your senses with Morena’s scrumptious delights.
